These lengths should be equal:
length explode  = 30
length exploden = 30
These lengths should be equal:
length explode2   = 22
length explodecn  = 22
length explode2uc = 22
length explode2lc = 22
compress explode = identity is true
compress int2id exploden = identity is true
in prin1 = identity is true

